Follow the official instructions to delete your account on the account settings page.
Confirm and agree to all terms of this agreement, while ensuring you meet the deletion requirements above.
We will review your account status and complete the deletion after a cooling-off period of 15 business days. (Please do not log in during the period, or your deletion request will be canceled.)
If the review or authentication fails, the deletion cannot be completed. You can follow the instructions for the next steps or contact customer support.
For any questions, feel free to email us at homelandhk@icloud.com. We are happy to help!
However, please note that if you log into and use the game with the account during the agreed deactivation processing period, you are deemed to have withdrawn your deactivation request. At the same time, you understand and agree that, before deleting or anonymizing personal information associated with the account, time is needed to appropriately organize and process the information to maximize the protection of your and other users' legal rights and interests. Therefore, there may be a delay in deleting or anonymizing the personal information associated with the account.
3.5 You understand and agree that during your request for account deactivation, if we need to verify related transactions, complaints, or other matters related to your account, or if we have other reasonable grounds, we reserve the right to freeze your deactivation request and suspend the deactivation services.
4. Others
4.1 This agreement is part of the User Agreement ("the main agreement"), and any matters not addressed in this agreement are applicable under the main agreement. In the event of any inconsistencies between this agreement and the main agreement, this agreement shall prevail. You also understand and agree that even if your game account is deactivated, it does not relieve or exempt you from any responsibilities you may need to bear under relevant laws, regulations, agreements, or rules.
4.2 The formation, effectiveness, execution, interpretation, and dispute resolution of the Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the country/region where the service operator is located (excluding
