Third-Party SDK Catalog Accessed by Fishing Frenzy: Sea World
1. Ruixue SDK
Third-party subject: Jilin Haiqi Technology Co., Ltd
Purpose of Use: To ensure your normal use of our services, to maintain the normal operation of the basic functions, to optimize product performance, to enhance your experience and protect your account security, and to achieve the purpose of inviting friends to play together.
