Welcome to Fishing Game Zone (hereinafter referred to as "the game") provided by [HOMELAND INTERACTIVE TECHNOLOGY & ENTERTAINMENT PTE. LTD.] (hereinafter referred to as "we")! In addition to the User Service Agreement, we will further explain to you in detail the collection, use, storage and sharing of personal information, and your rights and obligations in relation thereto through our Privacy Protection Policy (the "policy") when you use the Fishing Game Zone game.
If you are a minor, please read this policy with a guardian
.
Please read this policy carefully. When you tick the box, agree or use this game service, it is deemed that you are aware of the content of this policy and agree to sign this policy
.
1. Information we collect
In the course of your use of the Fishing Game Zone Game Service, we will collect information that you voluntarily provide or as a result of your use of the Service in the following manner, in order to provide you with and optimize our services and to protect the security of your account:
1.1 When you register or use the Fishing Game Zone game service, we will collect your
network identification information and personal device information
, which will be used to mark you as a user of the game. If you use a third-party platform and account to download and log in to Fishing Game Zone, we will collect your
unique identification, avatar and nickname
, which will be used to save your
login
information
so that you can log in on different devices.
In order to provide you with better game services and improve your gaming experience, we may collect your
nickname, avatar
,
operation information and game information
in Fishing Game Zone (hereinafter referred to as "such information", including but not limited to your
login status, battle information/status, and achievement information
) from your game account, and may show such information to you or other users. Depending on the game product, we may provide you with the relevant permissions so that you can choose whether to display the aforementioned information accordingly.
1.2 To comply with the relevant laws, regulations, policies, and requirements of the competent authorities in Vietnam, users of Fishing Game Zone are required to perform real-name authentication to continue accessing and enjoying the game. We will collect your
real-name identity information
(including
name and ID number
) only after obtaining your consent or when you voluntarily provide this information. This information is classified as sensitive. Refusal to provide real-name identity information may result in your inability to log in to the game or restrictions on using the game's certain features. If you are not a user located in Vietnam and will not be accessing the game in Vietnam, you may disregard this real-name authentication requirement.
1.3 To ensure the operation of our services, maintain the basic functionality of the game, optimize the performance of our game products, improve your gaming experience, and safeguard your account security, we will collect the following information:
your device ID, device name, device type and version, system version, IP address, device identifiers (such as IMEI/IDFA/OpenUDID/GUID/SIM card IMSI, MAC address), application ID, and network type
.
1.4 When you use the game service, we will collect your
game log information, such as login logs, item logs, game match information
, so that you can view your game history in the client, and also for the analysis of game operation statistics, customer service complaint handling and other game security analysis. You need to authorize the permission to write and read your
external storage
, which is used for reading and storing game data, downloading apk updates, and helping you to store and share exciting moments. In order to enhance your gaming experience, we may synchronize the aforementioned information to subsequent versions of the game or other products provided by us that you are using.
1.5 In order to ensure the safe and stable operation of the game and to realize certain functions, the game may access the
Software Development Kit (SDK) developed by a third party
. We will conduct security monitoring of the SDKs accessed by the game that involve the collection of personal information in order to ensure the security of your personal information. For details, please see the attached "Third Party SDK Catalog Accessed by Fishing Game Zone".
1.6 When you use the consumption function of this game, we will collect your
top-up record
and
consumption record information
so that you can inquire about your
transaction records
, and at the same time ensure the safety of your virtual items to the greatest extent possible.
Top-up records and consumption records
are sensitive information, and the collection of such information is necessary for the realization of the game's consumption function, otherwise the transaction will not be completed.
1.7 In order to ensure the security of your game account and create a fair, healthy and safe gaming environment, we will collect your
game identification information, hardware and operating system information, process and game crash record information
to combat behaviors that undermine the fair gaming environment or interfere with or disrupt the normal operation of the game services (e.g., for detecting piracy, scanning for external plug-ins, and preventing cheating, etc.).
1.8 When you
interact with other players through text, voice and other means
in the game, we might collect and save the content of
the above information
you send for filtering pornography, violence, politics, insults, malicious advertisements and other inappropriate content, in order to purify the gaming environment and maintain a healthy online environment.
1.9 If you wish to interact with other game players through voice, send questions and suggestions to us with screenshots. After obtaining your authorization, the game will access
your photos or storage files, microphone
, and provide you with screenshot saving, picture uploading, voice chatting and other functions.
1.10
Cell phone number and password
are personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you choose to use your cell phone number to register/activate your account. At the same time, we need your consent to access your
SMS reading permissions
. We will verify the validity of your identity by sending an SMS verification code.
1.11 If you want to contact the game customer service quickly by phone, the game will obtain your
phone call permission
to provide the in-game customer service system for you to directly call customer service after your authorization and consent.
1.12 In order to facilitate avatar providing and picture uploading for feedback, the game will access your
camera permission
and provide you with photo and screenshot storage functions after your authorization and consent.
1.13 If you want to recommend the game to your friends and family, the game will access your
contacts (read contacts)
to provide you with the game-sharing function after your authorization and consent.
1.14 If you wish to interact with nearby game players, we will collect your
geographic location information (e.g., IP address, GPS location, WLAN access point and Bluetooth that can provide the relevant information, and acquire sensor information)
to search for nearby game players, so as to allow you to match with and team up with nearby players. Geographic location information is sensitive information, and refusal to provide such information will only result in your inability to interact with nearby game players, but will not affect your normal use of other features of Fishing Game Zone, and you may cancel your authorization of
geographic location information
at any time.
1.15 In order to realize the purpose of inviting friends to play the game together, the game app will read your
clipboard data
when it starts, including
group ID, room ID, inviter ID and other information
.
1.16
In accordance with relevant laws and regulations and national standards, in the following cases, we may collect and use your personal information without asking for your authorization and consent:
1) Directly related to national security, national defense security, and other national interests; directly related to public safety, public health, public knowledge, and other major public interests.
2) Directly related to crime investigation, prosecution, trial, and judgment execution.
3) For the purpose of safeguarding the life, property, reputation, and other important legal rights and interests of you or other individuals, but it is difficult to obtain your consent.
4) The collected personal information is voluntarily disclosed to the public by yourself.
5) The personal information is collected from legitimate publicly disclosed information, like legitimate news reports, government information disclosure, and other channels.
6) Necessary for the conclusion and fulfillment of a contract at your request.
7) Necessary for maintaining the safe and stable operation of the products or services provided, such as discovering and processing product or service failures.
8) Necessary for carrying out legitimate news reporting.
9) Necessary for carrying out statistical or academic research in the public interest, and to de-identify personal information contained in the results of academic research or descriptions when they are provided to the public.
10) Other cases stipulated by laws and regulations.
