.
At present, except for collecting
game research information
from third-party research organizations to help us improve our game products, we will not actively obtain your personal information from third parties outside of this game. If we need to obtain your personal information indirectly from a third party outside the game for business development in the future, we will make clear to you the source, type, and scope of use of your personal information before obtaining it, and if we need to carry out personal information processing activities for conducting our business beyond the scope of the authorization and consent that you originally gave to the third party outside Fishing Game Zone for the provision of your personal information, we will obtain your explicit consent before processing your personal information. In addition, we will strictly comply with relevant laws and regulations and require the third party to ensure the legitimacy of the information it provides.
1.18 You (the user) understand and agree that in order to provide you with better products/services and experience, we may provide your
